    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Soft twill with a slightly napped surface, made in various weights of wool or soft cotton yarn, often in combination with synthetic yarn.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
